P\left(\frac{3}{2}X - \frac{n}{2} \geq 5\right) \Longleftrightarrow P\left(X \geq \frac{10+n}{3}\right) = \sum_{k = \lceil(10+n)/3\rceil}^n \binom{n}{k} \left(\frac{1}{4}\right)^k \left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^{n-k}
 = \left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^n \sum_{k =\lceil(10+n)/3\rceil}^n \binom{n}{k} \frac{1}{3^k}.
